  <h1>Welcome Customers</h1>
  Thanks for coming to learn more about the Calendar. While anyone with alpacas can sign up to be in the calendar we prefer to fill it with 
 advertising for existing customers, and of course we give you a discount.<br>
  <br>
   The 2012 Beautiful Alpacas Calendar is a 125-page full-color spiral-bound engagement calendar. WebArtists.biz created these calendars for 5 years and they were always a huge success! <br>
   <br> 

The 2012 Beautiful Alpacas Calendars will be sold online, at shows, and in stores. We will be getting these calendars in front of not just other alpaca ranches across North America but also thousands of non-alpaca owners. We are going to let everyone know how beautiful alpacas are, and why they should come see the ranches in the calendar!<br>
